text: Wilhelm Montag (born 24 March 1932) is a West German rower who represented the United Team of Germany. He competed at the 1956 Summer Olympics in Melbourne with the men's coxless four where they were eliminated in the semi-final. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:West German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United Team of Germany Category:Rowers at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Essen Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
